{"content":"<div style=\"LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none\"> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></span></b>&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">三峡拦洪30亿立方米 减轻中下游防洪压力</span></b></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"></span></b>&nbsp;</p>\n <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"> <p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三峡大坝从6月30日中午开始拦蓄洪水，截至7月3日18时，三峡已拦蓄水量约30亿立方米。按长江防总的统筹安排，三峡工程按31000立方米每秒控制下泄，最大削峰19000立方米每秒，削减洪峰40%。避免了长江上游洪水与中下游洪水叠加遭遇，有效减轻了长江中下游防洪压力。（来源：中国新闻网）</font></p> \n  <div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></span>\n  </div> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"> \n   <center>\n    <img style=\"WIDTH: 745px; HEIGHT: 489px\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.3g.gov.cn/file/2011.png\" width=\"773\" height=\"501\">\n   </center> \n   <center>\n    <font face=