{"content":"<div style=\"line-height: 150%\">\n <div style=\"LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none\"> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></span></span></b>&nbsp;</p> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"></span></span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">国务院三峡办举行迎新春茶话会祝福老同志</span></b></p> \n  <div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></span>\n  </div> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></p>\n  <font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"> \n   <hr align=\"center\" color=\"black\" SIZE=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noShade> </font>\n  <span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"> \n   <center>\n    <font size=\"3\">发布时间：2017-02-06</font>\n   </center><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o /-->\n    <o:p></o:p> <p><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -12pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\">本网消息：2017年1月22日，国务院三峡办举行迎新春茶话会，办党组书记、主任聂卫国介绍了三峡办2016年重点工作进展情况和2017年工作打算，并向老同志们致以新春祝福。三峡办副主任雷鸣山主持茶话会，魏廷铮、张德楠、雷加富等20余位离退休老同志出席茶话会。</font></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -12pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img style=\"WIDTH: 542px; HEIGHT: 361px\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.3g.gov.cn/file/2057.png\" width=\"657\" height=\"450\"></font></span></p><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\"></font></span></span></span>\n </div> \n <div style=\"LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none\">\n  <span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\"> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -12pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img style=\"WIDTH: 891px; HEIGHT: 515px\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.3g.gov.cn/file/2058.png\" width=\"1056\" height=\"624\"><br>　　茶话会上，老同志们以“为党和人民的事业增添正能量”为主题，畅谈发展变化、感受美好生活、建言三峡工作。整个茶话会在轻松、和谐、愉悦的氛围中进行，大家畅所欲言、各抒己见，对三峡各项工作充满信心和希望，同时提出了许多建设性意见和建议。</p> </font><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -12pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;<img style=\"WIDTH: 403px; HEIGHT: 249px\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.3g.gov.cn/file/2059.jpg\" width=\"1278\" height=\"720\">&nbsp;<img style=\"WIDTH: 423px; HEIGHT: 251px\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.3g.gov.cn/file/2061.png\" width=\"887\" height=\"536\"><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 同时，2017年春节前夕，国务院三峡办副主任雷鸣山、陈飞分别带领相关司负责同志走访慰问了钱正英、陈光健、黄友若、陈厚群、陆燕荪、石启荣、王武龙、张仁等与三峡工作相关的老领导、老同志，以及魏廷铮、陈家麟、唐章锦、罗长懋、段志德等三峡办部分离退休老同志，代表办党组向他们致以新春祝福和诚挚问候，感谢他们一直以来对三峡工作的关心和支持，把党中央和办党组的温暖带到了老同志的心头。（综合司、机关党委供稿）</font></p><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"></span></span>\n </div> \n <p><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font>&nbsp;</span></p> \n <p><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \"><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font>&nbsp;</span></p> \n <p><font size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"></font><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 1pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ａｓｃii-font-family: \">&nbsp;</span></p> \n <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24.75pt; LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -12pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n</div>","createTime":1518414836325,"modules":[],"pubTime":1486310400000,"sourceName":"国务院三峡工程建设委员会办公室","sourceType":1,"title":"国务院三峡办举行迎新春茶话会祝福老同志","url":"http://www.3g.gov.cn/3Gxxxq.ycs?GUID=6127"}
